item.title: Cologne redirection
item.description: function redirectToPage(url, manualRedirectionDiv, dryRun, debugInfo="") { if (manualRedirectionDiv) { // TODO: The below has no visible effect. manualRedirectionDiv.innerHTML = `Redirecting here`; } if (url && !dryRun) { window.location.replace(url + `?debugInfo=${debugInfo}`); } } let url = new URL(document.location.href); url. redirectToPage(window.location.href.replace("yaahi.github.io", "github.com/sanskrit-lexicon/csl-ldev/blob/main/v02"), document.getElementsByName("manualRedirectionDiv"), false);
